-- MOVES-Boutique investment bank Moelis appoints Philip Smith as MD
-- 
-- Mon Jul 28, 2014 08:51AM EDT
-- None



July 28 (Reuters) - Boutique investment bank Moelis & Co <MC.N> appointed Philip Smith as managing director to provide financial and strategic advice to industrial clients.

Smith will focus on the capital goods and automotive industries in the Europe, Middle East and Africa region. Smith, who was previously with Citigroup <C.N> in London and New York, has spent more than 17 years in the industry.